OVERVIEW
========

Homework #2 for CS324. A 2D graphics demonstration for Java.


DEPENDENCIES
============

To build and run this project, gradle must be installed and in the $PATH.


COMPILING
=========

Before building this project for the first time, gradle must be configured. The
following command will set everything up properly.

$ gradle wrapper

Once this is done, subsequent builds can be completed using the gradlew script.

$ ./gradlew build


RUNNING
=======

To run this project, use the gradlew script.

$ ./gradlew run


